{"tid":1229441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我今日係咪得自己一個出去？","createTime":"2019-06-16T02:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:35:13.000Z","uid":131782,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0534a30fb649e3881bca4dd552dd039e9cc2e0b7","tid":1229441,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"老母反對 家姐原本話出去 依家又話唔出<br />\n我成個屋企 得我自己為自由為香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我知道，我今日出去係唔會孤單，因為我知道仲有好多香港人同我一樣，都係會出黎㗎，係咪啊！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人，加油啊！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>林鄭，我屌你老母，暫你老母緩</strong></span><br />\n利申:以上所言係發夢夢見"},{"pid":"28f9a4a01a19cce8e131fe327432fe05795f8591","tid":1229441,"uid":15394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"唔係，仲有好多手足會同你一齊出"},{"pid":"f9871b98c441c7103d8f48618aa2eb37fbd675a0","tid":1229441,"uid":154763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"count me"},{"pid":"411afbe0370b99c493c5b2734018995ad1450071","tid":1229441,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"Gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bc1d2353251f810dcb9b0775fbd246075ba7f1","tid":1229441,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc79c1ebb8308fbf37c953d6f142897332c9713d","tid":1229441,"uid":138999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:48:41.000Z","msg":"依家係街 已經好多黑衫手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"